      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of character? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! It shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for great value. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a capable car that still has plenty of life and utility to offer!",
